---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Roof Repairs Highfields | Acreage Roofs & Reroofing"
  description="Roof repairs & reroofing in Highfields, Toowoomba — large acreage roofs, storm & hail damage, leak repairs, metal & Colorbond on the northern severe-storm corridor. QBCC-licensed. Free quote."
  canonical="https://toowoombaroofrepairs.com.au/highfields/">

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <span class="hero-eyebrow">Highfields &middot; northern growth &amp; acreage</span>
      <h1>Roof repairs &amp; reroofing in <span class="accent">Highfields</span>.</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        Highfields is the northern growth area above Toowoomba &mdash; larger
        acreage blocks, big roof areas, and a position right in the severe-storm
        corridor. Big roofs mean more to catch the hail and wind, and more to keep
        watertight. Leak repairs, storm and hail damage, restorations and full
        metal reroofs. QBCC-licensed.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a class="ph-cta btn btn-primary" href="/quote/" aria-label="Call us"><span aria-hidden="true">&#9742;</span> <span class="ph-text">Tap to call</span></a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/quote/">Get a free quote</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <span class="section-eyebrow">Why Highfields</span>
      <h2>Roofing the northern acreage country.</h2>
      <div class="divider"></div>
      <div style="max-width: 65rem;">
        <h3>Big roofs, big exposure.</h3>
        <p>
          Highfields homes tend to sit on larger blocks with bigger, more complex
          roof areas than the tighter inner suburbs &mdash; rural-residential and
          acreage builds, often with extended eaves, multiple roof planes and
          sheds and outbuildings as well. That&rsquo;s a lot of roof surface to
          keep watertight, and a lot of ridge line, valley and flashing where a
          storm can find a way in. We&rsquo;re set up for the bigger jobs as well
          as the small leak repairs.
        </p>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Squarely in the severe-storm corridor.</h3>
        <p>
          The northern Toowoomba growth area sits right in the path of the severe
          storms that track across the Downs through spring and summer. Golf-ball
          hail and damaging wind gusts are a recurring fact of life out here, and
          on a large acreage roof the damage can be extensive. We prioritise
          make-safe and tarping after a storm to stop water getting into the
          ceiling, then handle the insurance claim &mdash; see
          <a href="/services/storm-hail-damage/">storm &amp; hail damage</a> for
          how that runs.
        </p>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Metal makes sense on the big acreage roofs.</h3>
        <p>
          On large rural-residential roofs, Colorbond is usually the practical
          choice &mdash; it covers big areas efficiently, sheds storm water and
          hail melt fast, and wind-rated fixing to <strong>AS 1562.1</strong> and
          <strong>AS 1170.2</strong> stands up to the corridor&rsquo;s gusts.
          Whether it&rsquo;s a new shed roof, a leak on an existing one, or a full
          <a href="/services/metal-roofing/">Colorbond reroof</a> of the house,
          we work all of it. Many newer Highfields homes already have metal roofs
          that just need <a href="/services/roof-repairs/">repairs</a> after a
          storm.
        </p>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Typical Highfields jobs.</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Storm and hail damage make-safe and insurance-claim repair on a large acreage roof</li>
          <li>Leak repair on an extended-eave or multi-plane roof ($450&ndash;$1,200)</li>
          <li>Shed and outbuilding metal roof repairs and reroofs</li>
          <li>Re-bed and flexible-repoint ridge capping on a tile home ($1,800&ndash;$4,000)</li>
          <li>Full Colorbond reroof of a large rural-residential home ($25K&ndash;$35K+)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <h2>Other service areas.</h2>
      <div class="areas-grid">
        <a class="area-pill" href="/rangeville/">Rangeville</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/centenary-heights/">Centenary Heights</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/wilsonton/">Wilsonton</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/glenvale/">Glenvale</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/toowoomba-region/">All Toowoomba Region</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="cta-block">
        <h2>Free Highfields roof quote.</h2>
        <p>Acreage roof, shed, storm damage or a full reroof &mdash; we&rsquo;ll come out, look properly, and give you an honest price.</p>
        <div class="hero-actions" style="justify-content:center;">
          <a class="ph-cta btn btn-primary" href="/quote/" aria-label="Call us"><span aria-hidden="true">&#9742;</span> <span class="ph-text">Tap to call</span></a>
          <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/quote/">Get a free quote</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
